th=3D"2" stroke-linecap=3D"round" stroke-linejoin=3D"round"><path d=3D"M9 3=
H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4m6-6h10a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v4M9 3v18m0 0h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9M9 2=
1H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V9m0 0h18"></path></svg></a>
                    <span> Download our <a download=3D"" href=3D"https://ww=
w.1000minds.com/library/1000minds-ahp-example-tables.xlsx">free Excel workb=
ook</a> with the calculations outlined above.</span>
                </aside>
                <p>Thus, after squaring the matrix above, we have:</p>
                <figure class=3D"table-scroll-container">
                    <figcaption>Table 4: Squaring the matrix</figcaption>
                    <div class=3D"table-scroll-inner">
