                    </div>
                </figure>

                <p>Step 2 is much easier, just requiring us to sum each row=
 of the squared matrix to get a =E2=80=9Crow total=E2=80=9D for each row:</=
p>

                <figure class=3D"table-scroll-container">
                    <figcaption>Table 5: Add row totals</figcaption>
                    <div class=3D"table-scroll-inner">
                        <table class=3D"ahp-data ahp-criteria">
