                <p>Step 3 is to sum the =E2=80=9Crow totals and then divide=
 each =E2=80=9Crow total=E2=80=9D by sum. The resulting =E2=80=9Cpriority v=
ector=E2=80=9D (final column) corresponds to the criterion weights (summing=
 to 1).</p>

                <figure class=3D"table-scroll-container">
                    <figcaption>Table 6: Calculate the priority vector (wei=
ghts)</figcaption>
                    <div class=3D"table-scroll-inner">
                        <table class=3D"ahp-data ahp-criteria">
                            <tbody><tr>
                                <th></th>
