                </figure>

                <p>Step 4 is to square the squared pairwise comparison matr=
ix above, and repeat the earlier steps 1-3, resulting in this table and, mo=
st importantly, a slightly different set of weights:</p>

                <figure class=3D"table-scroll-container">
                    <figcaption>Table 7: Square the matrix again</figcaptio=
n>
                    <div class=3D"table-scroll-inner">
                        <table class=3D"ahp-data ahp-criteria">
                            <tbody><tr>
                                <th></th>
                                <th>Camera</th>
                                <th>Storage</th>
                                <th>Looks</th>
                                <th>Price</th>
